videos.headline: Iowa crowd waves to kids at children's hospital
videos.description: After the first quarter, the Iowa crowd continues their tradition of waving to the children in the nearby hospital.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Misc. (Iowa crowd waves to kids at children's hospital) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Hamler hurdles over Iowa defenders for a Penn State TD
videos.description: KJ Hamler makes the catch on third down, then leaps for the end zone to score a 22-yard touchdown for Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hamler hurdles over Iowa defenders for a Penn State TD) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Penn State gets great field position after Goodson's fumble
videos.description: Iowa's Tyler Goodson puts the ball on the ground, which ultimately sets up a Penn State field goal in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State gets great field position after Goodson's fumble) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Penn State drills Stanley, forces INT
videos.description: Penn State pressures Nate Stanley and forces the second Iowa turnover of the game on the interception.

videos.headline: Cain runs outside for a Penn State TD
videos.description: Noah Cain takes the pitch and scores the touchdown from five yards out to increase the Nittany Lions' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cain runs outside for a Penn State TD) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Smith Mosses defender for incredible Iowa TD
videos.description: Brandon Smith uses his opponent's helmet to help secure a sensational 33-yard touchdown for Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith Mosses defender for incredible Iowa TD) 2019/10/12
